{"id":506,"ayahs":[{"number":29,"arabic":"وَإِذْ صَرَفْنَآ إِلَيْكَ نَفَرًۭا مِّنَ ٱلْجِنِّ يَسْتَمِعُونَ ٱلْقُرْءَانَ فَلَمَّا حَضَرُوهُ قَالُوٓا۟ أَنصِتُوا۟ ۖ فَلَمَّا قُضِىَ وَلَّوْا۟ إِلَىٰ قَوْمِهِم مُّنذِرِينَ","translation":"AND LO! We caused a group of unseen beings to incline towards thee, [O Muhammad,] so that they might give ear to the Qur’an; and so, as soon as they became aware of it, they said [unto one another], “Listen in silence!” And when [the recitation] was ended, they returned to their people as warners.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4539.mp3","surahId":46,"words":[{"id":31658,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ কর)যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31659,"position":2,"arabic":"صَرَفْنَآ","translation":"আমরা আকৃষ্ট করে দিয়েছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31660,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَيْكَ","translation":"তোমার দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31661,"position":4,"arabic":"نَفَرًۭا","translation":"এক দলকে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31662,"position":5,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31663,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْجِنِّ","translation":"জিনদের","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31664,"position":7,"arabic":"يَسْتَمِعُونَ","translation":"তারা শুনতে পায়","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31665,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْقُرْءَانَ","translation":"কুরআন (তেলাওয়াত)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31666,"position":9,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31667,"position":10,"arabic":"حَضَرُوهُ","translation":"তারা সেখানে উপস্থিত হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/046_029_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31668,"position":11,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟"